from state Sens. Gary K. Hart (D-Santa Barbara) and Ed Davis (R-Northridge), 
and Assembly members Jack O'Connell (D-Carpinteria) and Cathie Wright (R-Simi 
Valley), said John Smart, university vice chancellor. 
