Witnesses told police they saw a suspect drive off in a maroon vehicle, which 
officers followed to a store at 13th Avenue and F Street, where Delbert 
Russworm, 35, was arrested. He was booked into County Jail on suspicion of 
murder, Clear said. 
</P>
