</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041890-0091 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 206014 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 18, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 12; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
