<P>
Marketing Program: On a more down-to-earth note, Catalina Marketing Group in 
Anaheim has announced Tuesday that it has signed the nation's fifth-largest 
supermarket chain to participate in the company's unique direct-marketing 
program. 
</P>
<P>
